<hymn_number>438</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Eden huona nupan tuokkhat,
 Na siem bang khan hun siem inla;
 Lei leh van vangpiekna haw chuh,
 A chunga-ah hun vuk zingin. (2)

[V2]
 2. Galili-ah Aw Lal Isu,
 Kichenna a Na um bang khan;
 A damsung u-a thilpha cheng,
 Uain-in hun suoksak zel inla. (2)

[V3]
 3. Pathien Thagau, a chung-u-ah,
 Na lungsietna'n nasem inla;
 Amau vengin gitloh apat,
 Thiengtho takin vawp zing inla. (2)

[V4]
 4. Nangma'n Na tundin loh le chuh,
 Athawn mai in hung chim untin;
 A kihehpihnau hihpung in,
 Nangmah ah hung bukim tau hen. (2)</lyrics>
<title>GOD'S PROVIDENCE</title>
</song>